    "long_instructions": "#### Treat Me\r\n\r\nRe-create the backing tracks for the verse and chorus of Treat Me by Chloe:\r\n- The verse has 3 tracks that are repeated twice\r\n- The chorus has 2 tracks that are repeated twice.\r\n\r\nAll the blocks you need are already in the workspace - you just need to connect them in the right order! Your final timeline should look like this:\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/38804da6afae06fd30ade0c9ac4dd2c3-image-1741021616619.png)",
